<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 05 Nov 2021 11:35:30 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>iPhone 13 爆 Mon 只可原廠維修，非官方更換屏幕無法使用 Face ID</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/8vlkZdZtrPI/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 05 Nov 2021 11:35:30 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[Face ID]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone 13]]></category><category><![CDATA[第三方維修]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1070034</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>早前有報導指出，iPhone 13 系列在第三方維修更換屏幕後很有可能遇到 Face ID 生物辨識功能無法 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">早前有報導指出，iPhone 13 系列在第三方維修更換屏幕後很有可能遇到</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Face ID </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">生物辨識功能無法使用的情況。近日就有外國網站成功研究到如何解決此問題，與寫入晶片的軟件解法不同，更偏向硬件維修的方式。惟該方法操作難度較高，第三方維修店較難處理。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070036" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Unable-toactivate-FaceID-1200x900-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Unable-toactivate-FaceID-1200x900-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Unable-toactivate-FaceID-1200x900-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Unable-toactivate-FaceID-1200x900-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070037" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1636077218-4adeb05b006b81d12c021bb3c6f1128a-694x366.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="366" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1636077218-4adeb05b006b81d12c021bb3c6f1128a-694x366.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1636077218-4adeb05b006b81d12c021bb3c6f1128a-768x405.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1636077218-4adeb05b006b81d12c021bb3c6f1128a.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">近日已有多方媒體確認，在最新推出的 iPhone 13 系列上會較容易出現「跣手」導致屏幕破損或故障，需要更換新的屏幕。但一旦需要進行更換維修，即使是將兩部 iPhone 的屏幕對調，也會遇到 Face ID 無法運行的情況。對此，外國網站 </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">iFixit 經研究後，日前終於找到解決方法——把負責溝通觸控的微型晶片拆下來安裝在新的屏幕上。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070038" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1636077306-dda4f89ffe748a282293bfbf8f725fc8-694x365.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1636077306-dda4f89ffe748a282293bfbf8f725fc8-694x365.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1636077306-dda4f89ffe748a282293bfbf8f725fc8-768x404.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1636077306-dda4f89ffe748a282293bfbf8f725fc8.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070039" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/iphone13_faceid_display_ic_169-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/iphone13_faceid_display_ic_169-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/iphone13_faceid_display_ic_169-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/iphone13_faceid_display_ic_169-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/iphone13_faceid_display_ic_169-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/iphone13_faceid_display_ic_169.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">貌似簡單，但實質上這卻是最難的一環。此項維修工作涉及到使用顯微鏡以及微型維修使用的焊接工具，導致維修屏幕新增的工序難度變得更高。但其實這只是第三方維修才需要的方法，官方授權維修其實只要透過軟件就能完成認證。換而言之，現時大部份的第三方維修店還是無法解決 Face ID 的問題，若 </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">iPhone 13 系列</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">用家不想支付官方高昂的維修費用，唯有使用防撞手機殼，盡量小心使用了。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_31390"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/m9MXlhsThmM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：</span><a href="https://www.ifixit.com/News/54829/apples-new-screen-repair-trap-could-change-the-repair-industry-forever"> <span style="font-weight: 400;">iFixit </span></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
