</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/8vlkZdZtrPI" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/05/apples-new-screen-repair-trap/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apples-new-screen-repair-trap</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>「元宇宙」中國或成最大贏家，台媒：中國一間廠佔全球 7 成 VR 代工</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/jF4GIAF1l6g/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 05 Nov 2021 09:49:23 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Facebook]]></category><category><![CDATA[Meta]]></category><category><![CDATA[元宇宙]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1069880</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>最近，Facebook 改名為 Meta，並宣布發展元宇宙（Metaverse），令元宇宙變成科技巨頭必爭之地 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>最近，Facebook 改名為 Meta，並宣布發展元宇宙（Metaverse），令元宇宙變成科技巨頭必爭之地。除軟件開發公司外，中國 VR （虛擬實景）代工大廠「歌爾聲學」亦因而受惠，股價大升。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069887 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot-2021-11-05-at-1.33.53-PM-694x469.png" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot-2021-11-05-at-1.33.53-PM-694x469.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot-2021-11-05-at-1.33.53-PM-1280x864.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot-2021-11-05-at-1.33.53-PM-768x519.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot-2021-11-05-at-1.33.53-PM.png 1373w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Facebook 改名前歌爾聲學股價</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069888 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot-2021-11-05-at-1.34.05-PM-694x476.png" alt="" width="694" height="476" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot-2021-11-05-at-1.34.05-PM-694x476.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot-2021-11-05-at-1.34.05-PM-1280x878.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot-2021-11-05-at-1.34.05-PM-768x527.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Screenshot-2021-11-05-at-1.34.05-PM.png 1348w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Facebook 改名後歌爾聲學股價</p><p>Facebook 創辦人朱克伯格表示，Meta 會是一個擁有 Facebook、Instagram、WhatsApp 等品牌的集團，當中，VR 裝置是達至元宇宙的必要條件，而中國 VR （虛擬實景）代工大廠「歌爾聲學」被外界認為是大贏家。研究機構 IDC 統計，去年 VR 市場頭 3 位品牌，分別是 Facebook 旗下的 Oculus、Sony 及 Pico，而全都交由中國公司代工，其中歌爾聲學則佔據 7 成的訂單，嚴重打擊台灣製造。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069882 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/62_2-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/62_2-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/62_2-506x900.jpg 506w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/62_2.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Facebook 創辦人朱克伯格宣布公司改名為 Meta</p><p>台灣電子 5 哥的高層分析，中國工廠能不計成本接單，而台灣工廠不能，VR 裝置製造量不及手提電腦和手機市場的 4%，「這時候考量虧損的風險，我們就不會硬去接訂單。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1069881 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/64.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="471" /></p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.businesstoday.com.tw/article/category/183015/post/202111030013/元宇宙題材只是「包裹商機糖衣的泡沫」？一文解析台廠為何在 VR 代工無存在感">今周刊</a></p><p>&#8212;</p>
