</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/jF4GIAF1l6g" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/05/goertek-inc/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=goertek-inc</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>木製機身蘋果電腦拍賣，評估高達 460 萬港元</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/5ZC8YB9LtkI/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 05 Nov 2021 09:26:32 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Chaffey College Apple-I]]></category><category><![CDATA[蘋果]]></category><category><![CDATA[蘋果電腦]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1069923</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>一部早期蘋果電腦將於美國加洲拍賣行 John Moran 拍賣，拍賣價為 20 萬美元（約 150 萬港元）。 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>一部早期蘋果電腦將於美國加洲拍賣行 John Moran 拍賣，拍賣價為 20 萬美元（約 150 萬港元）。這台由曾與 Steve Jobs 共同創辦蘋果公司的 Steve Wozniak 人手製作的電腦，被稱為 Chaffey College Apple-I，據說是因當年該校一名電子學教授購買，其後轉售級學生。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069926 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/577bbc53952d996-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/577bbc53952d996-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/577bbc53952d996.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069928 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/38abd75f2faf364-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/38abd75f2faf364-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/38abd75f2faf364.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069929 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/91c6c5fcc1cb848-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/91c6c5fcc1cb848-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/91c6c5fcc1cb848.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069930 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/0764ba80a63c526-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/0764ba80a63c526-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/0764ba80a63c526.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069931 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/988c354aee16be8-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/988c354aee16be8-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/988c354aee16be8.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>拍賣行清單顯示，Chaffey College Apple-I 配備原裝 Apple-1「NTI」主板，帶有原裝藍色 Sprague 39D 電容器、原裝電源調節器、罕見的原裝「Circle D」陶瓷電容器、Apple 盒式磁帶原裝 ByteShop Apple-1 koa 木箱中的適配器和 Datanetics 鍵盤，另外配上於 1986 年推出的螢幕。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069932 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/a374b8ca02327ff-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/a374b8ca02327ff-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/a374b8ca02327ff.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069933 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30ecdf04ccc500d-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30ecdf04ccc500d-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30ecdf04ccc500d.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069935 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/3fff65caa0eb34e-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/3fff65caa0eb34e-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/3fff65caa0eb34e.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069936 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/b3f6a4105e20ceb-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/b3f6a4105e20ceb-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/b3f6a4105e20ceb.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069937 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/b48afd28c742e19-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/b48afd28c742e19-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/b48afd28c742e19.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069938 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/def677256b3ad4d-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/def677256b3ad4d-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/def677256b3ad4d.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069939 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/483bf