ding="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069946 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/a33790be65a6710-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/a33790be65a6710-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/a33790be65a6710.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069947 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/c9be58b98d7c068-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/c9be58b98d7c068-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/c9be58b98d7c068.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1069948 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/568b71bf9d34199-694x555.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/568b71bf9d34199-694x555.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/568b71bf9d34199.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>拍賣行表示，已將機身打理好，而機能亦被鑑定和修復。經評估後，預計售價約 40 至 60 萬美金（約 300 至 460 萬港元）。該電腦將以「Chaffey College Apple-I」名義載入蘋果官方記錄。電腦將於太平洋時間 11 月 9 日上午 11 時 30 分開次拍賣。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.johnmoran.com/auction-lot/the-chaffey-college-apple-1-personal-computer_68148E4B12">John Moran</a></p><p>&#8212;</p>
