</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/0qoR5pyojOQ" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/05/adidas-xbox-360-forum-mid/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=adidas-xbox-360-forum-mid</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>DJI Mavic 3 新旗艦航拍機，香港售價 + 詳細規格</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/j7QoYT1IJbs/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 05 Nov 2021 02:30:07 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[航拍]]></category><category><![CDATA[dji]]></category><category><![CDATA[DJI Mavic 3]]></category><category><![CDATA[無人機]]></category><category><![CDATA[航拍機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1069745</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>DJI 今日正式發佈全新 DJI Mavic 3 系列旗艦航拍機，主打為消費級產品帶來極致影像拍攝效果。新機採 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>DJI 今日正式發佈全新 DJI Mavic 3 系列旗艦航拍機，主打為消費級產品帶來極致影像拍攝效果。新機採用 4/3 CMOS Hasselblad 相機，提供最大 28 倍混合變焦長焦距效果，更支援 Apple ProRes 442 HQ 編碼與內置 1TB SSD。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-02-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069759" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-02-1-694x412.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="412" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-02-1-694x412.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-02-1-1280x760.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-02-1-768x456.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-02-1-1536x912.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-02-1-2048x1215.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-02-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>消費級航拍機中超強畫質</h2><p>DJI 表示這部機加入了雙攝影系統，主相機有 4/3 CMOS Hasselblad L2D-20c 哈蘇相機。此相機採用 4/3 大尺寸感光元件，提升畫面解析力與更高的動態範圍，這部主相機為 f/2.8 至到 f/11 可變光圈相機，等效焦距為 24mm，帶來 84 度視角範圍，拍攝更廣闊景色。此相機支援自動對焦、原生 12.8 級動態範圍，保留更多影像亮部與暗位。這部相機更可與多個視覺感測器協作，利用感測器獲取的資 5 料，提高對焦速度。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-03-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069760" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-03-1-694x335.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="335" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-03-1-694x335.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-03-1-1280x617.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-03-1-768x370.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-03-1-1536x740.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-03-1-2048x987.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x1000-03-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>DJI Mavic 3 除主相機外，另外還配備另一個 162mm 長焦距相機，可帶來最大 28 倍混合變焦長焦距攝影。航拍機具有「探索模式」，能夠提前觀察前方景象，幫助創作者取景、規劃飛行路線更加輕鬆。</p><p>Mavic 3 支援 5.1K/50fps, 4K/120fps 的影像錄影，可說是消費級產品內高畫質、格率的產品，它支援 10bit D-Log 記錄多達 10 億種顏色，更好應對天空的色彩漸變層次，提供更大後製空間。</p><p>系列中的頂級型號 Mavic 3 Cine 支援 Apple ProRes 422 HQ 編碼，其資料傳輸率最大可達 3772Mbps，配合內置的 1TB SSD 儲存裝置，以及 10Gbps 高速傳輸線，有助將大容量影片從容記錄。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x440-03-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069762" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x440-03-1-694x516.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="516" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x440-03-1-694x516.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x440-03-1-1211x900.jpg 1211w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x440-03-1-768x571.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x440-03-1-1536x1141.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x440-03-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1000x440-01-scaled.jpg"><br /></a></p><h2>視覺感測器建構全新輔助系統</h2><p>DJI Mavic 3 內置有多個視覺感測器，配合視覺計算引擎，探測各方向上的障礙物。新機加入「高級智慧返航功能」，在飛行過程中視覺引擎會對周圍環境進行幾何掃描，當返航時，航拍機將自動計算出最佳路徑。飛行過程中 Mavic 3 更會測量環境風速狀況，根據風速與返航路徑，即時計算返航所需電量，令返航動作更為安全。Mavic 3 前視感知距離由上代 20 米提升至 200 米，令航拍機更早進行路徑動態調整狀態。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Waterfall_6000px-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069754" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Waterfall_6000px-694x284.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="284" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Waterfall_6000px-694x284.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Waterfall_6000px-1280x524.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Waterfall_6000px-768x315.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Waterfall_6000px-1536x629.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Waterfall_6000px-2048x839.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Waterfall_6000px-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Mavic 3 將使用最新 APAS 5.0 高級飛行輔助系統，以順暢規避多個方向上的障礙物。主機亦升級「智慧跟隨 5.0」功能，感測器與主攝鏡頭配合，令被攝主體始終處於攝影畫面的有效區域，令跟隨拍攝更自然，也支援前後左右對角線 8 個方向以及環繞飛行跟隨選擇。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CarDrifting_normal 副本.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069757" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CarDrifting_normal 副本-694x404.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="404" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CarDrifting_normal 副本-694x404.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CarDrifting_normal 副本-1280x744.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CarDrifting_normal 副本-768x447.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CarDrifting_normal 副本-1536x893.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CarDrifting_normal 副本.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>續航力提升</h2><p>DJI Mavic 3 針對機臂、機身與雲台曲面外形進行流線型減阻力設計，DJI 公佈新設計比對上代減少了 35% 風阻係數。另外航拍機壓縮了結構與硬體的重量佔比，採用更高能效馬達、槳葉與更大容量電池，令續航力達至 46 分鐘。電池也支援了 65W 快速充電，可在 90 分鐘充滿 5000mAh 電池。</p><h2>其他最新配件：</h2><p>DJI RC Pro 配備有附螢幕遙控器，最高亮度可達 1000 尼特。</p><p>DJI O3+ 可實現 15 公里超遠圖傳距離，即時傳輸 1080p/60fps 畫面，它可裝載 DJI Cellular 圖傳模組，在信號被樓宇、山丘或樹林遮擋時，可使用流動通訊傳輸</p><h2>DJI Mavic 3 三個版本售價、內容：</h2><p>DJI Mavic 3、DJI Mavic 3 暢飛套裝和更專業的 DJI Mavic 3 Cine 套裝。</p><h2>DJI Mavic 3</h2><p>售價 HK$17,099</p><p>包括：1 台航拍機、1 顆智能飛行電池、RC-N1 遙控器、3 對槳葉、收納保護罩等配件。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069756" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-694x438.png" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-694x438.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-1280x808.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-768x485.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-1536x969.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-2048x1292.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>DJI Mavic 3 暢飛套裝</h2><p>售價 HK$21,799</p><p>包括：1 台航拍機、3 顆智能飛行電池、RC-N1 遙控器、6 對槳葉、雙向充電管家、ND 濾鏡套裝（ND4/8/16/32）以及全新設計多功能收納包。</p><h2>DJI Mavic 3 Cine 大師套裝</h2><p>售價 HK$40,499</p><p>支援 Apple ProRes 422 HQ 編碼且配備內接式 1TB SSD 固態硬碟，DJI Mavic 3 Cine 大師套裝額外包括，内置帶屏幕遥控器 DJI RC Pro、高倍 ND 濾鏡套装（ND64/128/256/512）、10Gbps 高速傳輸線。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-Cin.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1069755" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-Cin-694x438.png" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-Cin-694x438.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-Cin-1280x808.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-Cin-768x485.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-Cin-1536x969.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-Cin-2048x1292.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Mavic3-Cin.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>保障專案 DJI Care</h2><p>適用於 DJI Mavic 3 的保障專案 DJI Care 同步開始提供。若飛行器意外失聯，只需同步飛行紀錄並使用遙控器成功認證飛丟意外，支付替換費用即可獲得同款產品。</p><p>DJI Care (DJI Mavic 3) 隨心換 1 年版售價 HK$1,949；</p><p>DJI Care (DJI Mavic 3 Cine 大師套裝) 隨心換 1 年版售價 HK$2,999，提供 1 年內 2 次低價替換權益</p><p>DJI Care (DJI Mavic 3) 隨心換 2 年版售價 HK$3,099；</p><p>DJI Care (DJI Mavic 3 Cine 大師套裝) 隨心換 2 年版售價 HK$4,999，提供 2 年內 3 次低價替換權益和第二年官方保固服務</p><p>資料來源：DJI, OTG</p></p><div class="feedflare">
